# 🏥 Hospital Management Database Schema

This document describes the structure of the Hospital Management Database designed using PostgreSQL.

---

# 📋 Departments

| Column Name | Data Type | Constraint | Description |
|-------------|----------|------------|-------------|
| department_id | INT | Primary Key | Unique department ID |
| department_name | VARCHAR(100) | NOT NULL | Name of the department |

---

# 👨‍⚕️ Doctors

| Column Name | Data Type | Constraint | Description |
|-------------|----------|------------|-------------|
| doctor_id | INT | Primary Key | Unique doctor ID |
| doctor_name | VARCHAR(100) | NOT NULL | Doctor's full name |
| specialization | VARCHAR(100) | NOT NULL | Medical specialization |
| department_id | INT | Foreign Key | References Departments |
| experience_years | INT | NOT NULL | Years of experience |
| salary | DECIMAL(10,2) | NOT NULL | Monthly salary |

---

# 🧑 Patients

| Column Name | Data Type | Constraint | Description |
|-------------|----------|------------|-------------|
| patient_id | INT | Primary Key | Unique patient ID |
| first_name | VARCHAR(50) | NOT NULL | Patient first name |
| last_name | VARCHAR(50) | NOT NULL | Patient last name |
| age | INT | NOT NULL | Patient age |
| gender | VARCHAR(10) | NOT NULL | Gender |
| blood_group | VARCHAR(5) | NOT NULL | Blood group |
| city | VARCHAR(100) | NOT NULL | City of residence |
| phone | VARCHAR(15) | NOT NULL | Contact number |
| admission_date | DATE | NOT NULL | Admission date |

---

# 📅 Appointments

| Column Name | Data Type | Constraint | Description |
|-------------|----------|------------|-------------|
| appointment_id | INT | Primary Key | Unique appointment ID |
| patient_id | INT | Foreign Key | References Patients |
| doctor_id | INT | Foreign Key | References Doctors |
| appointment_date | DATE | NOT NULL | Appointment date |
| appointment_time | TIME | NOT NULL | Appointment time |
| diagnosis | VARCHAR(200) | NOT NULL | Diagnosis |
| status | VARCHAR(30) | NOT NULL | Appointment status |

---

# 💊 Medicines

| Column Name | Data Type | Constraint | Description |
|-------------|----------|------------|-------------|
| medicine_id | INT | Primary Key | Unique medicine ID |
| medicine_name | VARCHAR(100) | NOT NULL | Medicine name |
| manufacturer | VARCHAR(100) | NOT NULL | Manufacturer |
| unit_price | DECIMAL(10,2) | NOT NULL | Price per unit |

---

# 📝 Prescriptions

| Column Name | Data Type | Constraint | Description |
|-------------|----------|------------|-------------|
| prescription_id | INT | Primary Key | Unique prescription ID |
| appointment_id | INT | Foreign Key | References Appointments |
| medicine_id | INT | Foreign Key | References Medicines |
| dosage | VARCHAR(100) | NOT NULL | Dosage instructions |
| quantity | INT | NOT NULL | Quantity prescribed |

---

# 💳 Bills

| Column Name | Data Type | Constraint | Description |
|-------------|----------|------------|-------------|
| bill_id | INT | Primary Key | Unique bill ID |
| appointment_id | INT | Foreign Key | References Appointments |
| consultation_fee | DECIMAL(10,2) | NOT NULL | Consultation fee |
| medicine_cost | DECIMAL(10,2) | NOT NULL | Medicine cost |
| laboratory_charges | DECIMAL(10,2) | NOT NULL | Laboratory charges |
| total_amount | DECIMAL(10,2) | NOT NULL | Total bill amount |
| payment_method | VARCHAR(30) | NOT NULL | Payment method |
| payment_status | VARCHAR(20) | NOT NULL | Payment status |
| bill_date | DATE | NOT NULL | Bill date |

---

# 🔗 Database Relationships

- One **Department** can have many **Doctors**.
- One **Doctor** can have many **Appointments**.
- One **Patient** can have many **Appointments**.
- One **Appointment** can have many **Prescriptions**.
- One **Medicine** can appear in many **Prescriptions**.
- One **Appointment** has one **Bill**.

---

# 🗂️ Database Overview

| Table | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| Departments | Stores hospital departments |
| Doctors | Stores doctor information |
| Patients | Stores patient records |
| Appointments | Stores appointment details |
| Medicines | Stores medicine information |
| Prescriptions | Stores medicines prescribed during appointments |
| Bills | Stores patient billing information |
